GTTimeStampExplicit_st Struct Reference
[Verification]

This structure represents the explicit data extracted from a timestamp.

Field Documentation

char* GTTimeStampExplicit_st::cert_issuer_name

Certificate issuer name.

char* GTTimeStampExplicit_st::cert_serial_number

Certificate serial number, in base 16.

char* GTTimeStampExplicit_st::certificate

Public key certificate, in base 32. Normally NULL for long-term hash-linked timestamps.

char* GTTimeStampExplicit_st::content_type

CMS ContentInfo content type. Currently always "1.2.840.113549.1.7.2", for PKCS#7 CMS SignedData.

int GTTimeStampExplicit_st::digest_algorithm

Digest algorithm used for the signature. See GTHashAlgorithm for possible values.

int GTTimeStampExplicit_st::digest_algorithm_count

Count of entries in the list of digest algorithms.

int* GTTimeStampExplicit_st::digest_algorithm_list

List of digest algorithms used in the CMS message. See GTHashAlgorithm for possible values.

char* GTTimeStampExplicit_st::encap_content_type

CMS EncapsulatedContentInfo content type. Currently always "1.2.840.113549.1.9.16.1.4", for PKCS#9 TSP TSTInfo.

int GTTimeStampExplicit_st::hash_algorithm

The algorithm used to produce the data hash. See GTHashAlgorithm for possible values.

char* GTTimeStampExplicit_st::hash_value

The hash value submitted to be timestamped, in base 16.

int GTTimeStampExplicit_st::history_count

Count of entries in the hash chain that describes the provenience path from the aggregation round to publication.

GTHashEntry* GTTimeStampExplicit_st::history_list

The hash chain that describes the provenience path from the aggregation round to publication.

int GTTimeStampExplicit_st::issuer_accuracy

Precision of the gateway clock, in milliseconds.

char* GTTimeStampExplicit_st::issuer_name

Timestamp issuer service name. NULL if not present in the timestamp.

GT_Time_t64 GTTimeStampExplicit_st::issuer_request_time

The time when gateway received the request for the timestamp.

int GTTimeStampExplicit_st::key_commitment_ref_count

Count of entries in the list of key commitment references.

char** GTTimeStampExplicit_st::key_commitment_ref_list

List of key commitment references, in UTF-8.

int GTTimeStampExplicit_st::location_count

Count of entries in the hash chain that describes the location of the timesource within the GuardTime network.

GTHashEntry* GTTimeStampExplicit_st::location_list

The hash chain that describes the location of the timesource within the GuardTime network.

char* GTTimeStampExplicit_st::nonce

The nonce from the timestamping request, in base 16. NULL if not present in the timestamp.

char* GTTimeStampExplicit_st::pki_algorithm

PKI signature algorithm ID. Either both or neither of pki_algorithm and pki_value are present. Currently, if present, always "1.2.840.113549.1.1.11", for id-sha256WithRSAEncryption.

char* GTTimeStampExplicit_st::pki_value

PKI signature, in base 16. Either both or neither of pki_algorithm and pki_value are present.

char* GTTimeStampExplicit_st::policy

GuardTime timestamping policy ID.

int GTTimeStampExplicit_st::pub_reference_count

Count of entries in the list of publication references.

char** GTTimeStampExplicit_st::pub_reference_list

List of publication references, in UTF-8.

int GTTimeStampExplicit_st::publication_hash_algorithm

The algorithm used to compute the publication hash value. See GTHashAlgorithm for possible values.

char* GTTimeStampExplicit_st::publication_hash_value

Publication hash value, in base 16.

GT_Time_t64 GTTimeStampExplicit_st::publication_identifier

Publication ID.

char* GTTimeStampExplicit_st::serial_number

Timestamp serial number, in base 16.

char* GTTimeStampExplicit_st::signature_algorithm

GuardTime timestamping algorithm ID. Currently always "1.3.6.1.4.1.27868.4.1", for GuardTime TimeSignature algorithm.

int GTTimeStampExplicit_st::signed_attr_count

Count of entries in the list of signed attributes.

GTSignedAttribute* GTTimeStampExplicit_st::signed_attr_list

List of signed attributes.

int GTTimeStampExplicit_st::signed_data_version

Version of the CMS SignedData structure. Currently always 3.

int GTTimeStampExplicit_st::signer_info_version

Version of the CMS SignerInfo structure. Currently always 1.

int GTTimeStampExplicit_st::tst_info_version

Version of the CMS TSTInfo structure. Currently always 1.
